    <li><strong>Antioxidant shield</strong> — rich in carotenoids and polysaccharides that help protect liver cells from free-radical damage.</li>
    <li><strong>Mitochondrial support</strong> — helps maintain cellular energy production for detox workloads.</li>
    <li><strong>Balanced immune tone</strong> — polysaccharides help modulate overactive responses that can inflame liver tissue.</li>
  </ul>

